<HEADLINE> Cohen Offers Help for Russian Sub Rescue </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 15 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Defense Secretary
William Cohen made an offer to his Russian counterpart for the
rescue of the crew of a sunken Russian submarine, the Pentagon
said Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
