more than 50 units including the provincial Federation of Literary
and Art Circles, Yunnan Daily, the Yunnan People's Publishing
House, the provincial Xinhua Bookstore Group Co. Ltd, the
provincial Beijing Opera Institute and provincial Film Studio for
Nationalities, and some individual workers in the cultural
industry.
</P>
