cultural industry and businessmen under different kinds of
ownership to develop the province's cultural industry and expand
international exchanges and cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Yunnan is a region where dozens of Chinese minority ethnic
groups inhabit and has abundant resources of different cultures.
It has hosted a series of large cultural events such as World
Horticulture Expo, International Art Festival and International
Tourist Festival in the provincial capital of Kunming. 
