<HEADLINE> Syrian, Qatari Leaders Hold Talks in Damascus </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAMASCUS, August 15 (Xinhua) -- Syrian President Bashar Al-Assad
held talks at People's Palace with visiting Qatari Emir Sheikh
Hamad bin Khalifa al-Thani shortly after the emir arrived here
Tuesday afternoon.
</P>
<P>
The two leaders discussed regional and bilateral issues of
common concern in the meeting which was also attended by high
ranking officials from both countries. Then the two leaders turned
away for a meeting in camera.
