<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 15 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 15 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
August 16, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station this
evening:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 23 degrees C., max. 33 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 22 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 24 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 22 degrees C., max. 35 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
