CDL Ho headed the losers of the day incurring a loss of 246
cents to close at 0.96 Hong Kong dollars. DBS sank 50 cents to
finish at 22.5 Singapore dollars while SPH gave up 40 cents to end
at 28.9 Singapore dollars. 
