<HEADLINE> Global Tour of Painting Exhibition To Return To China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 15 (Xinhua) -- A group of historic paintings on
the Nanjing Massacre will be exhibited in Beijing's China
Revolutionary Museum from Aug. 18 to Sept. 10 after being
exhibited around the world.
</P>
<P>
Some 700,000 people visited the exhibition which has been held
in nearly 20 countries, including the U.S., Germany, France,
Britain, Singapore and Brazil.
</P>
<P>
The painter, Li Zijian, was born in 1954 in south China's Hunan
province. He was famous by his painting series on human nature
and love.
</P>
<P>
Historical records indicate that at least 300,000 Chinese were
butchered and more than 20,000 women raped by Japanese invaders in
December 1937, known as the "Nanjing Massacre".
</P>
<P>
The exhibition will also go to other major Chinese cities like
Shanghai, Guangzhou and Changsha. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE20000815.0164 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-15 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Bank Increases Individual Consumption Loans </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 15 (Xinhua) -- The Agriculture Bank of China (
ABC), one of China's four State-owned commercial banks, said today
its individual consumption loans have risen by a big margin during
the January-June period this year.
</P>
<P>
A spokesman with ABC said the bank's individual housing loans
has increased 8.1 billion yuan this year to hit 23.4 billion yuan
by June, an annual increase of 74.5 percent.
</P>
<P>
Automobile consumption loans amounted to 1.5 billion yuan by
the end of June, taking the second largest share among the four
State-owned commercial banks.
</P>
<P>
Other individual consumption loans, such as education loans,
loans to purchase agricultural equipment, tourism loans, durable
goods consumption loans, all witnessed a hefty increase as well.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman noted that ABC's housing loans had maintained a
steady and healthy development over the past six months due to
efforts paid on the quality of loans. ABC also expanded its
businesses by providing clients with new housing services, he said.
</P>
<P>
To minimize risks, ABC has been keeping a strict eye on the
qualification of auto distributors and purchasers, with the surety
gained via interim agencies and insurance companies.
</P>
<P>
Currently, the newly added individual consumption loans
accounted for some 10 percent of ABC's all new loans. 
</P>
</TEXT>
